\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/c4ae1d07e7ac12e4d223115b56aaec98.poster.avif?t=1717385342\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/c4ae1d07e7ac12e4d223115b56aaec98.webm?t=1717385342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/c4ae1d07e7ac12e4d223115b56aaec98.mp4?t=1717385342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Perform fun dances to swing tunes as your quest for fame begins!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/47d9f57fabba679611ef9f0250912f3f.poster.avif?t=1717385342\" width=540 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/47d9f57fabba679611ef9f0250912f3f.webm?t=1717385342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126630/extras/47d9f57fabba679611ef9f0250912f3f.mp4?t=1717385342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Avoid capture by Green Star, an energy company seeking to use child labor in their factories! <br><br>Oh, my.</h2></h2></strong></h2>",
